node.title: Late Night Doesn’t Feel Great About Omicron
node.alt: “Reminds me of that famous sugar-free gum slogan: ‘Four out of five dentists agree: What’s the point of chewing gum? Death comes for us all,’” Colbert said.
node.description: Moderna’s chief executive said scientists anticipate Omicron is “not going to be good.” Stephen Colbert called the sentiment “not comforting.”
node.content: ["Welcome to Best of Late Night, a rundown of the previous night\u2019s highlights that lets you sleep \u2014 and lets us get paid to watch comedy. Reminds me of that famous sugar-free gum slogan: \u2018Four out of five dentists agree: What\u2019s the point of chewing gum?
